=== Phase 1 Multiplayer Demo ===

🌐 P2P NETWORKING ENABLED
   - Auto-discovery via mDNS (localhost)
   - Player state sync @ 20 Hz
   - Voxel operations with CRDT
   - Ed25519 signatures
   - World state persistence

Controls:
  WASD - Move
  Space - Jump (walk) / Up (fly)
  Shift - Down (fly mode)
  F - Toggle Walk/Fly mode
  E - Dig voxel (10m reach)
  Q - Place voxel (10m reach)
  T - Send test chat message
  Mouse - Look around (click to grab)
  ESC - Release mouse
  F12 - Take screenshot

